             sworn. - This day se'nnight, in the middle of the day, as I was passing just on this side <placeName id="t17981024-6-crimeloc32">Temple-bar</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17981024-6-crimeloc32" type="placeName" value="Temple-bar"></interp>
